data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming ranch-style residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the rest of the home, making it an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. Escape to the tranquility of your private oasis with a large fenced-in backyard. A convenient shed, complete with a window A/C unit, adds versatility to the space, providing a cozy retreat or a practical workspace for various hobbies. Strategically located near military bases and NASA, this home is not only a haven but also offers proximity to career opportunities and exciting adventures.
